<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">manhood</ENAMEX> is at stake, the "<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">N</ENAMEX> word" is verboten in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Washington</ENAMEX>. On <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Sunday</TIMEX>'s
