<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">days ago</TIMEX>, when a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">reporter</ENAMEX> asked about the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">N</ENAMEX> word, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">White House</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">spokesman</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Joe</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lockhart</ENAMEX> answered, "We have a military objective now, which is to bring
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">President</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Milosevic</ENAMEX> to meet these conditions that we have laid out." By calling
