<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>. Diplomacy. Like negotiation, this word
smells of weakness. Again, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">administration</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">officials</ENAMEX> deflect it by contrasting
