<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Madeleine Albright</ENAMEX> and her <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">spokesman</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Jamie Rubin</ENAMEX>, are fond of the same
